/* ───────────────────────── Switzerland POI dataset ─────────────────────────
   Curated points of interest across all 26 cantons of Switzerland for the
   sightseeing route planner. Researched with parallel agents and verified
   against Wikipedia / Wikimedia Commons (coordinates, elevations, images).
   129 POIs.

   Schema (single-letter keys mirror passes-data.js for compactness):
     n      name                                 (string)
     la, lo latitude, longitude                  (decimal degrees, 5 dp)
     e      elevation in metres                  (number, optional)
     region geographic region                    (see REGIONS below)
     cat    primary category                     (see CATEGORIES below)
     themes cross-cutting interest tags          (array)
     access how to get there                     (subset of car/cable-car/cogwheel/funicular/train/boat/foot)
     season when to visit                        (subset of spring/summer/autumn/winter)
     dur    typical visit duration (hours)       (number)
     sc     notability score (1-10)              (10 = unmissable, 7 = excellent, 5 = solid, 3 = niche)
     td     short description                    (≤250 chars)
     rs     why-visit rationale                  (≤200 chars)
     wl, wt Wikipedia language code + title
     bp     hero photo URL (Wikimedia Commons)

   CATEGORIES:
     mountain-summit      Mountain summit / cable‑car peak
     alpine-lake          Alpine or scenic lake
     waterfall-gorge      Waterfall or gorge
     glacier              Glacier viewpoint or experience
     old-town             Heritage old town / UNESCO city
     castle-fortress      Castle or fortress
     monastery-church     Abbey, monastery or notable church
     scenic-railway       Scenic railway line / cog / funicular as POI
     bridge-engineering   Bridge or engineering marvel
     village              Charming village worth its own visit
     national-park        National park / nature reserve
     spa-wellness         Thermal spa / wellness town
     viewpoint-panorama   Panoramic viewpoint / observation deck
     museum-cultural      Museum / cultural site
     geology-cave         Cave / geological feature
     wine-region          Wine region / vineyard landscape
     special-experience   Other unique experience

   REGIONS (POI counts):
     Valais                        23
     Bernese Oberland              17
     Central Switzerland           16
     Ticino                        14
     Engadin                       11
     Vaud / Lake Geneva            10
     Eastern Switzerland           10
     Graubünden                     8
     Bern / Emmental                5
     Basel / Aargau                 5
     Jura / Neuchâtel               4
     Zürich                         4
     Fribourg                       2

   THEMES (filter / multi-select):
     unesco, family-friendly, summer-only, winter-sport, year-round,
     swimmable, photogenic, panoramic-view, cable-car, cogwheel-railway,
     car-accessible, hike-required, boat-accessible, historic, architecture,
     food-drink, iconic, hidden-gem, spa-wellness, special-experience.
*/

